snippet.title: Street Fighter 4rd Strike AE - All New Supers
snippet.description:
All new Super Moves exclusive to:

Street Fighter 4rd Strike AE (3rd Strike Balance Mod)

You can find the game here and play it with Fightcade 2 online with people!

https://discord.com/invite/ZZ962cT

Edit: Akuma has another III super that is up, up, up + KKK buttons; Twelve has a 2nd III Super which is a counter-move that is done by pressing down, down, PP, I forgot those sorry.
